precis:
Grant of a leave of absence to three judges who will participate in the
National Judicial Study Leave Fellowship Program from July 1, 1990 until
December 31, 1990.
  1. Mr. Justice Edward D. Bayda
     Chief Justice of Saskatchewan
  2. Mr. Justice Marcel Nichols
     Puisne Judge of the Court of Appeal of Quebec
  3. Mr. Justice Paul Reeves
     Puisne Judge of the Superior Court of Quebec
